Correct!

For questions 3 and 4, divide using long division.

  1. \((m^3+1000) \div (m+10)\)

Correct!

Try again. Revisit activity 6.3.2.

The correct answer is \(m^2-10m+100\).

  1. \((125y^3-64) \div (5y+4)\)

Correct!

Try again. Revisit activity 6.3.2.

The correct answer is \(25y^2-20y+16- \frac{128}{5y+4}\).

For questions 5 and 6, divide using synthetic division.

  1. \((b^3-3b^2-4b+12) \div (b+2)\)

Correct!

Try again. Revisit activity 6.3.3.

The correct answer is \( b^2-5b+6\); remainder \(0\).

  1. \((3x^4-11x^3+2x^2+10x+6) \div (x-3)\)

Correct!

Try again. Revisit activity 6.3.3.

The correct answer is \(3x^3-2x^2-4x-2\); remainder \(0\).
